## Your buyers already ask AI for recommendations

Ask ChatGPT for the best provider in your market and the answer names two or three businesses. Either you are one of them or a competitor is. There is no page two in an AI answer.

Across the 60+ sites I track in Google Analytics, AI assistants now send four-figure quarterly traffic to the best performer, with more than 90% of it coming from ChatGPT. The sites that win those citations share specific, fixable traits: clear entity signals, consistent facts about the business everywhere they appear, and content structured so an AI can lift the answer cleanly.

**Fixed fee: £495.** Delivered in 5 working days. If you go on to work together, the audit fee is credited against your first month.

## What the audit covers

### Citation baseline

Your 20 most commercially important queries run across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Bing Copilot, Gemini, and Google AI Overviews. Each response recorded: whether you are cited, how you are described, which sources the assistant relied on, and which competitors appear instead.

### Competitor citation analysis

The audit traces why competitors win each query: the third-party pages the assistant sourced, the review and directory presence backing them up, and the content structures being quoted.

### Entity and consistency audit

AI assistants cross-check facts about your business across the open web before repeating them. Conflicting names, phone numbers, addresses, or service descriptions make assistants hesitate or blend you with a competitor. The audit maps every inconsistency and ranks each correction by impact.

### Content extractability and technical review

The review checks whether your pages let an assistant lift a clean quotable answer: heading hierarchy, direct answer placement, schema markup quality, llms.txt, and crawler access for AI user agents. Each issue comes with the specific fix.

### 90-day plan, tracking, and walkthrough call

A prioritised 90-day plan scored by revenue impact against effort, GA4 configuration to separate AI assistant referrals from the rest of your traffic, and a 45-minute walkthrough call to agree your first 30 days of work.
